{
  "stem": "13382.2",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And when they discovered that I got ulcer, I mean, it was-- everybody here was astonished.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "This is impossible.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Something must be wrong with someone.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So I stayed in the hospital and was cared very well.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Well-- and I became quite a celebrity, because all the physicians from Bratislava-- they came, and they wanted to see me.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[LAUGHTER]",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "You know, is it possible?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So I was there for a while, and I was taught how to-- how to look after myself and also-- but I definitely-- I couldn't leave home.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So I had to be back home.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And that was a problem, because there was a very strong gap in my education.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I remember I had to go back for the second year high school.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I had to go back to Bratislava, because by the way, during-- in the morning, we learned the Jewish studies, and in the afternoon, we learned into the high school, right?",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So I-- six months I did not have a chance to learn, and I still passed the second year high school.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So that was the end of my study, because I came back to Fil'akovo, right?",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I was already-- I couldn't even go into Lucenec, because I was sick.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So I just read and-- everything which I-- is in front of me, and I was sort of teaching myself.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And mother was very helpful.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "She, you know-- I had some problem, I always ask her then.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So that was my education.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It's-- it's amazing to-- to say.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I fitted in with the non-Jewish community very well.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I mean, from the-- from the-- from the elementary school, I never had any problem.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I always was accepted by them.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I have quite a lot of friends-- non-Jewish friends.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
